## 🔄 How Integration Works

```
User Action (Click)
      ↓
Frontend fetch() call
      ↓
HTTP Request → Backend API (localhost:3001)
      ↓
Express handles route → Mongoose queries MongoDB
      ↓
JSON Response sent back
      ↓
Frontend renders data on DOM
```

---

## 🚀 How to Run

```bash
# Step 1 — Start the backend (Project 3 folder)
cd Project-3
npm install
node server_db.js
# Backend runs at http://localhost:3001

# Step 2 — Open frontend in browser
# Just open menu_manager.html in any browser!
# (No extra setup needed for frontend)
```

